r4859 | antanas | 2017-02-03 16:02:00 +0200 (Fri, 03 Feb 2017) | 8 lines

cod-tools/ (antanas@kurmis)
Refactoring: changing the validation messages are printed.
Instead of printing multiple instances of the same message,
the script now print a single instance of the message
posfixed with the number of times the message has been
raised. If the message has only been raised once, the
postfix is omitted.

