done in revision 4783.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r4783 | andrius | 2016-12-06 15:25:28 +0200 (Tue, 06 Dec 2016) | 7 lines

trunk/
Returning an empty list of datablocks upon parsing empty CIF files in both
C and Perl parsers. According to the CIF specification, empty CIF is an
empty list of datablocks. Moreover, this is done in order to skip
processing of initial empty datablock in 'for (@$data) { ... }'
constructions.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r4782 | andrius | 2016-11-28 14:49:23 +0200 (Mon, 28 Nov 2016) | 5 lines

trunk/
Appending ${LIBFLAGS} to the generation of SO file in Makefile for Perl
bindings of C CIF parser in order to ease external linking, for example,
against libcodcif.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r4781 | andrius | 2016-11-25 15:07:15 +0200 (Fri, 25 Nov 2016) | 6 lines

trunk/
Bugfix: performing all character operations via int data type (instead of
char) in cif_lexer.c, as conversions between char and int used to cause
loss of EOF characters (see https://latedev.wordpress.com/2012/12/04/all-about-eof/
for reference).

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r4780 | andrius | 2016-11-25 12:57:58 +0200 (Fri, 25 Nov 2016) | 3 lines

trunk/
Removing svn:executable property from AuthorNames.pm.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r4779 | andrius | 2016-11-25 11:30:42 +0200 (Fri, 25 Nov 2016) | 6 lines

trunk/
Putting external libraries to LIB_DIRS in Makeconf, just as is done in
Makefile-based system of 'codcif' component. Placing the routines to build
external libraries in Makelocal-SWIG-module, again based on 'codcif'
Makefile.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
