r4777 | andrius | 2016-11-25 09:50:58 +0200 (Fri, 25 Nov 2016) | 6 lines

trunk/
Merging recipe for 'make clean-SWIG-module' in 'make cleanAll-SWIG-module'
recipe, since 'make clean; make' resulted in complete recompilation, while
only removal of temporary files/test diffs are usually requested with
'make clean'.

