r4647 | andrius | 2016-05-06 11:48:58 +0300 (Fri, 06 May 2016) | 5 lines

trunk/
Detecting empty datablock name as error in C CIF parser, since empty names
are not allowed by CIF v1.1 grammar. Error can be overridden via
'fix_datablock_names' parser option.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
